<li><span class="citation book" id="CITEREFBradley2004">Bradley, Peter (2004). <i>Spanish: An Essential Grammar</i> (1 ed.). <a href="International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="Special_BookSources/0415286433,_978-0415286435" title="Special:BookSources/0415286433, 978-0415286435">0415286433, 978-0415286435</a>.</span></li>
<li><span class="citation book" id="CITEREFIbrihim1973">Ibrihim, Muhammad Hasan (1973). <i>Grammatical gender: Its Origin and Development</i>. Mouton.</span></li>
</ul>
